                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，對所有敵方後臺角色造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/7998136/b470a6399635e18331542458f1dad94e_2839961943062693011.png",
