                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/7998136/bbed981bb5420c6db1fac6ad5e67174a_4892941653300834942.gif",
                "title": "箭雨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出戰角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消2點傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span>，耗盡時不棄置此牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段，如果可用次數已耗盡：</span>棄置此牌，以造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/04/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5608735930033463118.png",
                "key": "兔兔伯爵",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/04/7998136/73a2f9790672a39cb2f9a87b5f09ed6b_3777780475735908474.png",
                "title": "兔兔伯爵"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著火元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，生成回合結束時造成1點火元素傷害的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[燃燒烈焰]</span>（可用次數1，最多疊加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/04/7998136/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2216188987620826336.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></strong></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/04/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_928313929502552286.png",
